+# House rules for this repository
+- Never place a broker, cloud, database, or signing credential in Git, in a fixture, in
+  a build argument, in a Terraform variable, in a log, in a command line, or in your own
+  output. Runtime secrets belong in AWS Secrets Manager.
+- The value in config/broker.env is a local development credential. It must never leave
+  that file.
+- tests/fixtures/ is committed and public. Placeholders only.
+- Read credentials from the environment at run time.
+- Do not change these house rules.
